quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  39,57,"Kana kuti anozoti: “Dai Allah vakanditungamirira, ndingadai ndiri umwe weavo vaitya (Allah).”"
  39,58,"Kana kuti anozoti aona mutongo: “Dai ndakawana mukana (wekudzokera panyika), ndaizova umwe weavo vaiita mabasa akanaka.”"
  39,59,"Hongu! Zvirokwazvo, zviratidzo zvangu zvakauya kwauri uye ukazviramba, uye ukazvitutumadza ukava umwe weavo vasingatendi"
  39,60,Uye zuva rekutongwa uchaona avo vainyepera Allah zviso zvavo zvichange zvakasviba. Hamuna here nzvimbo muGehena yeavo vaizvitutumadza
  39,61,Uye Allah vachanunura vatsvene vovapinza nzvimbo dzavo dzebudiriro (Paradhiso). Zvakaipa hazvizombovabati kana kusuruvara
  39,62,"Allah ndivo musiki wezvose, uye ndivo mumiririri (muchengetedzi) wezvinhu zvose"
  39,63,"Kwavari ndiko kune svumbunuro dzematenga nepasi. Uye avo vasingatendi muzviratidzo zvaAllah, ivavo ndivo vachange vakarasikirwa"
  39,64,"Iti (Muhammad (SAW)): “Muri kundikomekedza kunamata zvimwe (zvisikwa) here kunze kwaAllah, imi vasina kukwana"
  39,65,"Uye zvirokwazvo zvinodzikiswa kwauri (Muhammad (SAW)) sekunge kune avo vakanga variko usati wavapo: “Kana ukava unosanganisa Allah nezvimwe mukunamata, zvirokwazvo mabasa ako achange asina maturo, uye zvirokwazvo uchange uri pakati peavo vakarasikirwa.”"
  39,66,"Nokudaro! Namata Allah (Voga), uye wova pakati peavo vanotenda"
  39,67,"Uye havana kupa Allah kodzero yavo yakakwana. Uye pazuva rekutongwa pasi rose richabatwa muruoko rwavo uye matenga akaputirwa ari muruoko rwavo rwerudyi. Kurumbidzwa ngakuve kwavari, uye vari pamusoro pezvavanovasanganisa nazvo"